msgstr "Kuidas paigaldada"

msgid ""
"Place .ttf/.otf files in ~/.local/share/fonts/ then run 'fc-cache -f -v' and "
"refresh this list."
msgstr ""
"Paigalda .ttf/.otf failid kausta ~/.local/share/fonts/ ja seejärel käivita "
"'fc-cache -f -v' ning värskenda seda nimekirja."

